- ✅ `GeneratedRegex` used for 3 core patterns (L13, L16, L19)
- ✅ `IsAllUpperCase` uses `foreach` loop instead of LINQ `.All()`
- ✅ `Slugify` uses `ToLowerInvariant()` correctly
- ✅ `IsAsciiAlphanumeric` / `WordCount` use allocation-free iteration

